The role of computer hardware and operating systems in IT support.

  The role of a IT employee is to ensure that computer hardware is up to date and funcioning. The IT support and operating systems needs to be up and running at all time to make a business function.
  The role can include things from replacing PC components like monitors,mice and keyboards to routers servers and switches. 
  Their is also the digital part to making sure machines are recieving and transmitting data and stying connected. Without the role of a computer hardware and operating systems IT rol then most business
  would fail to function due to almost everthing being on the internet. 
